Converted from the [C# mission script found in release-20131223](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/release-20131223/OpenRA.Mods.RA/Missions/Allies02Script.cs).

It follows the original script pretty closely, there are only a few minor deviations. That also means that the difficulty is quite high, and I'll probably end up introducing a new "Easy" skill level and shifting the other two up accordingly. I'll need some feedback on that, however.

